{"word":"ἐμός","slug":"ἐμός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n34194\" key=\"e)mo/s\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἐμός</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ή</itype>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">όν</itype>, possess. Pron. of <per opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"per\">1st pers.</per>: (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ἐγώ, ἐμοῦ</etym>):—<sense id=\"n34194.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">mine</tr_>; <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"var\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ contr.\">contr.</a></gram> </gramGrp> with the Art., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οὑμός, τοὐμόν, τοὐμοῦ, τὠμῷ, τἀμά</foreign>, Trag. (not Com., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τἀμὰ γὰρ διοίχεται</foreign> is paratrag. in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg010.perseus-grc1:393\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ec.\">Ec.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">393</biblScope> </bibl>), rarely in Prose, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">οὑμός</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg036.perseus-grc1:354c\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ep.\">Ep.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">354c</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τἀμά</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg008.perseus-grc1:258b\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href